<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Pawan Passi was the head of equity syndicate a=
t Morgan Stanley. Big banking clients =E2=80=94=C2=A0corporations, private =
equity firms =E2=80=94=C2=A0would sometimes come to Morgan Stanley for bloc=
k trades, saying =E2=80=9Cwe=E2=80=99re going to sell a big block of stock =
in Company X after the close today and we will want a bid from you, but don=
=E2=80=99t tell anyone, this is highly confidential.=E2=80=9D Passi would t=
hen <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34992007.28535=
3/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDEtMTYvb=
W9yZ2FuLXN0YW5sZXktbGVha2VkLXNvbWUtYmxvY2stdHJhZGVzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA0MTAyNF9N=
T05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJ=
tPTI0MDQxMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3a6bd9=
cd" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">call some of his favorite hedge fund customers</a> and say =E2=
=80=9Chey, there=E2=80=99s a big block of Company X coming after the close =
today, get ready.=E2=80=9D The hedge funds would then short the stock, know=
ing that they would be able to buy at a discount in the block trade and mak=
e a quick profit. Morgan Stanley would be better positioned to win the bloc=
k trade, because it had already lined up buyers (the hedge funds). Good for=
 Morgan Stanley, good for Passi, good for the hedge funds.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bad for the client =E2=80=94=C2=A0the seller o=
f the block =E2=80=94=C2=A0who expected=C2=A0Morgan Stanley to keep the dea=
l confidential and who probably got a lower price on the trade.<a class=3D"=
footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorati=
on: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000=
; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transparent !impo=
rtant; display: inline-block;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a>=C2=A0Eventually this was discovered, Passi was fired, Morgan Stanley <=
a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34992007.285353/aHR=
0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9uZXdzL3ByZXNzLXJlbGVhc2UvMjAyNC02/607f07ceef4b8524a=
319a23cB3970e7db" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"=
_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-b=
ottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid;=
 background-color: #ccc;">paid a big fine</a>, Passi paid a smaller fine an=
d was banned from the securities industry for a year, and presumably the Mo=
rgan Stanley clients whose block trades were leaked =E2=80=94=C2=A0<a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34992007.285353/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDEtMTYvYmxhY2tzdG9uZS1v=
YWt0cmVlLWJ1cm5lZC1ieS1tb3JnYW4tc3RhbmxleS1zLWJsb2NrLXRyYWRlLWxlYWtzP2NtcGl=
kPUJCRDA0MTAyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbG=
V0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDQxMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b85=
24a319a23cBc778850c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">firms like Blackstone, Oaktree and Cinven</a>=
=C2=A0=E2=80=94=C2=A0were mad about it, though when Bloomberg News asked th=
em they declined to comment.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-2=
" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-=
width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !import=
ant; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[2]</span>
</a></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand, presumably the hedge fund c=
ustomers were pleased with the customer service they got from Passi, and sa=
d to see it end. <em>They</em> were <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/34992007.285353/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlua=
W9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDItMDgvYmlsbC1hY2ttYW4td2FudHMteW91ci1tb25leT9jbXBp=
ZD1CQkQwNDEwMjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2x=
ldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDA0MTAmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b85=
24a319a23cB55e9fda7" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">never accused of wrongdoing</a>, and they got=
 to keep their profits. =E2=80=9CI know who my daddy is,=E2=80=9D one of th=
em told Passi. And now Bloomberg=E2=80=99s=C2=A0Sridhar Natarajan, Ava Benn=
y-Morrison, and Katherine Burton <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/34992007.285353/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2Fy=
dGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDQtMTAvbW9yZ2FuLXN0YW5sZXktYmFua2VyLXBhd2FuLXBhc3NpLWpvaW5=
zLWZpcm0tdGhhdC1nb3QtaGlzLWJsb2NrLXRyYWRpbmctbGVha3M_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQxMDI0X0=
1PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlc=
m09MjQwNDEwJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd5b705=
f0" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">report</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A former Morgan Stanley banker who was punishe=
d in the block-trading probe that rattled Wall Street joined one of the fir=
ms that was the recipient of confidential information he leaked.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Pawan Passi was hired by Frank Fu=E2=80=99s Ca=
aS Capital Management, according to people familiar with the matter. CaaS m=
ade its name partnering with banks as they sought buyers for block trades, =
becoming one of the biggest US funds dedicated to buying big chunks of stoc=
ks.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I love it.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"=
#footnote-3" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: n=
one !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-b=
lock;">
<span>[3]</span>
</a>=C2=A0Really the least they could do! Presumably Passi=E2=80=99s knowle=
dge of the block trade market will be helpful to a block trade specialist. =
But also developing a reputation for helping out down-on-their-luck equity =
syndicate bankers should be helpful to a block trade specialist. If your bu=
siness is partnering with banks for block trades, being nice to the bankers=
 might encourage more banks to partner with you.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Honestly though this story would be funnier if=
 Passi turned up, not at CaaS or one of the other hedge funds he helped, bu=
t at Blackstone or Oaktree or one of the other private equity firms he=C2=
=A0<em>harmed</em>. Really Blackstone should hire him as its head of block =
trades. On the one hand, probably bad incentives. On the other hand, he kno=
ws all the tricks.=C2=A0</p>
