r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;">from Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Todd Gillespie</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A cadre of McKinsey &amp; Co. consultants stro=
de into a meeting with Houston=E2=80=99s most prominent local bank to dwell=
 on the problem bedeviling thousands of regional banks: How to stay relevan=
t.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThe thing that I laugh at, though, is=
 they had a chart,=E2=80=9D said Steve Stephens, the CEO of Amegy Bank, rec=
alling the presentation to the board of its parent company in late 2022. Mc=
Kinsey=E2=80=99s message was that banks such as Amegy could find a lucrativ=
e business niche, like the so-called specialty regional banks that it spotl=
ighted in slides, he said.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CWell, that was First Republic, Silico=
n Valley Bank and Signature,=E2=80=9D said Stephens, all of which collapsed=
 last year. =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s specialization that got them.=E2=80=9D</p=
>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This was good advice, that McKinsey gave him!<=
a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-4" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transp=
arent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[4]</span>
</a>=C2=A0Find a niche, specialize, make a big bet: Diversification makes y=
ou safer but reduces the variance of your returns; specialization increases=
 the variance and thus the likelihood of making a lot of money for sharehol=
ders. Also the likelihood of going to zero.</p>
